                              OpenDict ChangeLog
			      ==================

0.5.7
-----
o Dictionaries editor improved
o Dictionaries manager improved
o Ability to install dictionaries from the Internet added
o Better unicode support
o Works only using wxPython 2.5
o Lots of bug fixes


0.5.8
-----
o Makefile tries both pygettext and pygettext.py (for Fedora linux)
o Small bug fixes

